This is the root directory of PSCF C++/Cuda package. See the README.md
file for basic instructions on usage.

Subdirectories:
  bin/       default installation directory for executables
  bld/       build directory for out-of-source builds 
  data/      read-only data files (i.e., space group description files)
  docs/      documentation, including some web manual source files
  examples/  example input files for simple computations
  lib/       scripts written in python, matlab or other languages
  make/      makefiles & makefile fragments to be installed by setup script
  src/       C++ and CUDA source code files

Files: 
  CONTENTS  - this file
  LICENSE   - GNU GPL v3 license
  README.md - brief intro to package (as displayed on github page)
  makefile  - main makefile for out-of-source compilation and cleanup
  setup     - executable script to set up build system prior to compilation

